A Streamlit-based interactive web application that uses the MET Museum Open API and GPT-based AI models to generate professional-level curatorial explanations for artworks related to Ancient Greek mythology.

Users can explore mythological figures, view real museum artworks, and receive AI-generated curatorial analyses.

